messages.speech: UtkalHacks is dedicated to providing a safe and comfortable environment and harassment-free experience for everyone, regardless of gender, gender identity, and expression, age, sexual orientation, disability, physical appearance, body size, race, ethnicity, nationality, religion, political views etc. It's important because Hackathons are about solving problems, and it's our responsibility to provide inclusive environments where all genders can flourish. Now emisha is conducting the hackathon in Ravenshaw university.
